April Reyes’s boss
We prefer an HOA, Community pool is not a necessity but nice to have. Here is a wish list I put together:

Wish list:
-Single Family Home
-3 bedrooms plus den or office space 
-2+ baths
-Min 1500 sq ft
-decent sized backyard must have some grass or turf, cannot be all hardscape
-updated kitchen/baths
-Hardwood or laminate wood floors. 
-2 stories preferred 
-2 car garage
-community HOA (with pool preferred)
-family friendly neighborhood 
-I know it’s weird but I want a pantry and indoor laundry!!

I think we discussed the following areas: 92123, 92124, 92126, 92127, 92128, 92129, 92131, Rancho Penasquitos, Poway, Santee(?), Escondido (?), we haven’t ever been to Santee or Esco so not sure if we would like it. May consider Allied Gardens (92119) and Del Cerro (92120)
